---
title: Parmesan Chive Chicken & Potatoes Mixed Greens & Honey Dijon Dressing
description: Skip over the question of what to make tonight, and jump right into this quick-cooking, stress-free chicken dinner that’s on the table in 15 minutes. All you have to do is prep a simple salad, sizzle up juicy chicken cutlets with a speedy Parmesan-chive sauce made in the same pan, and let the microwave work its magic on buttery garlic-herb potatoes. And just like that, you’re a kitchen hero.
